Class ModifyFileClient

java.lang.Object
javafx.application.Application
ModifyFileClient
public class ModifyFileClient
extends javafx.application.Application
JavaFX Application that lets you open and create files. When run in conjunction with the a server running on port 5000, the save function sends the file to the server for storage in memory.
Author:
Wil Simpson
